{"tid":972580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本億萬富豪前澤友作發帖豪派1億日圓，刷新Twitter轉推紀錄","createTime":"2019-01-07T13:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T03:52:30.000Z","uid":12609,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"644e7b55649fe1be0695fea912eb1f3af9ccc4ac","tid":972580,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2019/1/5bv855pfolxcdxxpk7nyf9leqiphqy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F1%2F5bv855pfolxcdxxpk7nyf9leqiphqy.jpg&h=13f86b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本億萬富豪前澤友作（Yusaku Maezawa）於1月5日在Twitter宣布「派錢」，刷新史上最多人轉推的Twitter帖文紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n前澤友作是日本著名購物網ZOZOTOWN的社長，他在1月5日在Twitter表示，為慶祝ZOZOTOWN在聖誕新年期間錄得100億日圓銷售，會在他的帳號追隨者中隨機揀出100位網友，分享1億日圓獎金，即每人獲派100萬日圓（約7.2萬港元／台幣28.6萬元）。參加方法是「成為我的追隨者及轉推這則帖文。」他會在1月7日後以短訊形式通知得獎者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yousuck2020/status/1081544630754103296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyousuck2020%2Fstatus%2F1081544630754103296&d=OQn54MhRhb3uFRN17xZq%2FttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=41a57521\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyousuck2020%2Fstatus%2F1081544630754103296&h=eaca543e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yousuck2020/status/1081544630754103296</a>"},{"pid":"40746daf27883781c15bd2728a2efe4d77c3271d","tid":972580,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"黃思聰上次派幾多"},{"pid":"2782023ccd45ee9908d7bc2d34f89b9057a98883","tid":972580,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪會多咗好多僵屍粉絲囉"},{"pid":"cad2daf2b7e12a817bc870c30ec9bf88b4e708a3","tid":972580,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40746daf27883781c15bd2728a2efe4d77c3271d","tid":972580,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0